	  </figure></para><exercise id="secfhsst_id2240"><title> Critical Angle 1 </title>
          <problem id="probfhsst_id2241">
          <para id="id188495">Given that the refractive indices of air and water are 1 and 1,33, respectively, find the critical angle. </para>
          </problem>
          <solution id="solfhsst_id2244"> <list id="listfhsst_id2244" list-type="enumerated" number-style="arabic" class="stepwise">
          <item> <label> Determine how to approach the problem </label>
          <para id="id188520">We know that the critical angle is given by:</para>
          <equation id="id188524">
            <m:math overflow="scroll" mode="display">
              <m:mrow>
                <m:msub>
                  <m:mi>θ</m:mi>
                  <m:mi>c</m:mi>
                </m:msub>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:msup>
                  <m:mo form="prefix">sin</m:mo>
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                    <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                  </m:mrow>
                </m:msup>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                  <m:mfrac>
                    <m:msub>
                      <m:mi>n</m:mi>
                      <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                    </m:msub>
                    <m:msub>
                      <m:mi>n</m:mi>
                      <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                    </m:msub>
                  </m:mfrac>
                  <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </equation>
          </item> <item> <label> Solve the problem </label>
          <equation id="id188583">
            <m:math overflow="scroll" mode="display">
              <m:mtable displaystyle="true">
                <m:mtr>
                  <m:mtd columnalign="right">
                    <m:msub>
                      <m:mi>θ</m:mi>
                      <m:mi>c</m:mi>
                    </m:msub>
                  </m:mtd>
                  <m:mtd>
                    <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  </m:mtd>
                  <m:mtd columnalign="left">
                    <m:mrow>
                      <m:msup>
                        <m:mo form="prefix">sin</m:mo>
                        <m:mrow>
                          <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                          <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                        </m:mrow>
                      </m:msup>
                      <m:mrow>
                        <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                        <m:mfrac>
                          <m:msub>
                            <m:mi>n</m:mi>
                            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                          </m:msub>
                          <m:msub>
                            <m:mi>n</m:mi>
                            <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                          </m:msub>
                        </m:mfrac>
                        <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                      </m:mrow>
                    </m:mrow>
                  </m:mtd>
                </m:mtr>
                <m:mtr>
                  <m:mtd/>
                  <m:mtd>
                    <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  </m:mtd>
                  <m:mtd columnalign="left">
                    <m:mrow>
                      <m:msup>
                        <m:mo form="prefix">sin</m:mo>
                        <m:mrow>
                          <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                          <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                        </m:mrow>
                      </m:msup>
                      <m:mrow>
                        <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                        <m:mfrac>
                          <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                          <m:mrow>
                            <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                            <m:mo>,</m:mo>
                            <m:mn>33</m:mn>
                          </m:mrow>
                        </m:mfrac>
                        <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                      </m:mrow>
                    </m:mrow>
                  </m:mtd>
                </m:mtr>
                <m:mtr>
                  <m:mtd/>
                  <m:mtd>
                    <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  </m:mtd>
                  <m:mtd columnalign="left">
                    <m:mrow>
                      <m:mn>48</m:mn>
                      <m:mo>,</m:mo>
                      <m:msup>
                        <m:mn>8</m:mn>
                        <m:mo>∘</m:mo>
                      </m:msup>
                    </m:mrow>
                  </m:mtd>
                </m:mtr>
              </m:mtable>
            </m:math>
          </equation>
          </item> <item> <label> Write the final answer </label>
          <para id="id188715">The critical angle for light travelling from water to air is <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mrow><m:mn>48</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>∘</m:mo></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math>.
 </para>
          </item> </list> </solution>
</exercise>
