          <para id="id188820">The critical angle for water is <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mrow><m:mn>48</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>∘</m:mo></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math>.</para>
